# https://github.com/hedronvision/bazel-compile-commands-extractor
# The license for this is generally permissive, but requires any publicly published changes to be pushed back to the main repo:
# https://github.com/hedronvision/bazel-compile-commands-extractor/blob/main/LICENSE.md
